column2: select b.year, p.nameFirst, p.nameLast, b.HR, b.rank from (select yearId as year, playerId, sum(hr) as HR       ,      rank() over (partition by yearid order by sum(hr) desc) as rank           from baseball.batting b           group by yearId, playerId) b   ,     baseball.players p  where p.playerid=b.playerid    and b.rank <= #  order by b.year desc, b.rank
